Package: pR
Type: Package
Title: Support functions for the analysis of pupillary response data
Version: 0.01
Date: 2013-07-07
Author: Hedderik van Rijn, Jacolien van Rij
Maintainer: Hedderik van Rijn <hedderik@van-rijn.org>
Description: A set of functions that can assist by the analysis of pupillary
    response data. Functionality includes blink detection, downsampling,
    filtering & smoothing, and some analysis code. Package uses data.table
    syntax extensively to speed up processing of the (potentially) huge data 
    sets.
License: LGPL
Depends: data.table, zoo
Collate:
    'blinkstatistics.R'
    'detectblinks.R'
    'downsample.R'
    'expandblinks.R'
    'interpolateblinks.R'
    'normalize.R'
    'plotblinkdiagnostics.R'
    'pr-package.R'
